HEADWORD: Bowery
<hw>Bow"er*y</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Shading, like a
bower; full of bowers.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A <qex>bowery</qex> maze that shades the purple streams.</q>
<rj><qau>Trumbull.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
